OL,3,CWorkers rally outside Amazon warehouse
OL,4,Cas 'historic' union ballot takes place
OL,6,FAmazon workers at a warehouse in
OL,7,FLongtown, near Carlisle, are rallying
OL,8,Fwith colleagues around the country as
OL,9,Fa ballot opens that could see the
OL,10,Fonline giant recognise a trade union
OL,11,Ffor the first time in the UK.
OL,13,FMore than 3,000 employees are expected
OL,14,Fto take part in a ballot at their
OL,15,FCoventry site which could force Amazon
OL,16,Fto negotiate pay, terms and conditions
OL,17,Fwith the GMB Union.
