OL,3,CWorkers rally outside Amazon warehouse
OL,4,Cas 'historic' union ballot takes place
OL,6,FAmazon workers will begin voting in
OL,7,Fwhat the union call a "historic and
OL,8,Flegally binding vote" on whether to be
OL,9,Frepresented by a union.
OL,11,FRecognition would mean the online
OL,12,Fretail giant would have to negotiate
OL,13,Fwith the GMB Union on terms, pay and
OL,14,Fconditions for workers.
OL,16,FAmanda Gearing, GMB Senior Organiser,
OL,17,Fsaid: "This is a historic moment.
OL,19,F"Amazon is one of the world's most
OL,20,Fhostile and anti-union employers.
