OL,3,CWorkers rally outside Amazon warehouse
OL,4,Cas 'historic' union ballot takes place
OL,6,F"They're a multi-billion-pound global
OL,7,Fcompany investing huge energy to
OL,8,Fresist efforts by working-class people
OL,9,Fto fight for a better life.
OL,11,F"But workers have rejected Amazon's
OL,12,Fattempts to smash their union.
OL,14,F"Instead, they've stood up to be
OL,15,Fcounted and demanded the chance to
OL,16,Fvote on union recognition.
OL,18,F"Now Amazon workers, now the bosses,
OL,19,Fwill decide".
