OL,3,CWorkers rally outside Amazon warehouse
OL,4,Cas 'historic' union ballot takes place
OL,6,FAmazon said that its employees have
OL,7,Falways had the choice of joining a
OL,8,Funion.
OL,10,FAn Amazon spokesperson said: "Our
OL,11,Femployees have the choice of whether
OL,12,For not to join a union. They always
OL,13,Fhave.
OL,15,F"Across Amazon, we place enormous
OL,16,Fvalue on having daily conversations
OL,17,Fand engagement with our employees.
OL,19,F"It's a strong part of our work
OL,20,Fculture. We value that direct
OL,21,Frelationship and so do our employees."
